OOC: Oh, ok, no problem then.

::Hot Rod/Prowl/Epyon/Skyburst::

They all go silent and look at Hot Rod, with puzzled faces.

"Guys, I'm as clueless as you," states Hot Rod.

Prowl steps up.
"Well since we are all Maximals here..."
He looks at Hot Rod and Skyburst.
"...and Autobots, I suggest we not fight anymore. However I will not
just hand Hot Rod over too you."

Hot Rod moves up.
"What's with this story, dragons? I've never seen you before today.
There is no way in hell I ever lead you."
